metadata.name: Find Your Flock
metadata.description:
Find Your Flock, an inside look at FWB FEST 2022 located in Idyllwild, CA. 

For three days on a mountain, global members of Friends With Benefits enjoyed a music and art experience at the intersection of friendship + technology. The festival featured live music, a curated art show, food & beverage program, and academic discussions...all reflective of the community's ever expanding interests. Filmed by FWBTV.
